CREATE TABLE autoIncreamentEntity (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  createdAt BIGINT NULL,
  name VARCHAR(255) NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY(id)
);


CREATE TABLE compositeIdEntity (
  sid VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  uid VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  balance BIGINT NOT NULL,
  name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY(sid, uid)
);


CREATE TABLE decimalEntity (
  id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  createdAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  updatedAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  version BIGINT NOT NULL,
  balance DECIMAL(10,4) NULL,
  name VARCHAR(100) NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY(id)
);


CREATE TABLE enumEntity (
  id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  createdAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  updatedAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  version BIGINT NOT NULL,
  roleName VARCHAR(50) NULL,
  name VARCHAR(100) NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY(id)
);


CREATE TABLE todos (
  id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  createdAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  updatedAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  version BIGINT NOT NULL,
  f_Target_date DATE NULL,
  targetDateTime DATETIME NULL,
  address VARCHAR(100) NULL,
  f_name VARCHAR(100) NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY(id)
);


CREATE TABLE user (
  id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  age INTEGER NULL,
  createdAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  updatedAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  version BIGINT NOT NULL,
  score DOUBLE NULL,
  email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  the_tag VARCHAR(255) NULL,
  CONSTRAINT UNI_NameEmail UNIQUE (name, email),
  INDEX IDX_TagId (the_tag),
  CONSTRAINT UNI_name_the_tag UNIQUE (name, the_tag),
  PRIMARY KEY(id)
);
